>\n* Established a [[Royal Commission of Inquiry into Historical Abuse in State Care]]<ref name=\"Tax cuts NZH\" />\n* A new generation [[SuperGold Card|SuperGold smart card]] with entitlements and concessions<ref name=\"Coalition deals revealed\" />\n* Remove \"excessive\" benefit sanctions<ref name=\"Coalition deals revealed\" />\n* Eliminate the [[gender pay gap]] within the public sector<ref name=\"Coalition deals revealed\" />\n\n===Transport and Infrastructure===\n* Re-allocate spending towards rail and cycling infrastructure, and road safety improvements<ref name=\"Coalition deals revealed\" />\n* Establish light rail to [[Auckland Airport]] and to West Auckland<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/politics/95488637/jacinda-ardern-promises-light-rail-to-auckland-airport |title= Jacinda Ardern promises light rail to Auckland Airport |publisher= Stuff (Fairfax) |date=6 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Orsman|first1=Bernard|title=Labour plans regional fuel tax to fund trams to airport, West Auckland|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&objectid=11936797|accessdate=4 November 2017|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=26 October 2017}}</ref>\n* Commuter rail in 18 months to Hamilton<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.stuff.co.nz/waikato-times/news/95999367/labour-promises-rail-within-18-months-for-hamilton-commuters |title= Commuter rail from Auckland to Hamilton |publisher= Stuff (Fairfax) |date=21 August 2017}}</ref>\n* Commuter rail to Hamilton and Tauranga<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/politics/95985999/labour-to-spend-20m-on-commuter-rail-between-auckland-hamilton-and-tauranga |title= Commuter rail from Auckland to Hamilton, Tauranga for $20 million |publisher= Stuff (Fairfax) |date=17 August 2017}}</ref>\n* Commuter rail for Christchurch<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/politics/93960723/labour-commits-to-christchurch-commuter-rail-in-100m-package |title= Commuter rail fo